    When to use kerasilk taming balm?
    I use this daily and apply about a size of a quarter, rub it around on my hands first then apply evenly throughout my hair before drying and straightening. I like that it is not greasy and it is not a thick heavy cream. This taming balm is lightweight and adds shine and combability to the hair.
